OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,FJohn Stones is leaving Manchester City
OL,7,Fat the end of the season after a
OL,8,Fdecade at the club.
OL,10,FThe 31-year-old will depart the Etihad
OL,11,FStadium when his contract ends in the
OL,12,Fsummer of 2026.
OL,14,FStones was one of Pep Guardiola's
OL,15,Ffirst signings in 2016 and has made
OL,16,Fnearly 300 appearances for City,
OL,17,Fhelping the club win 19 major
OL,18,Ftrophies, including six Premier League
OL,19,Ftitles and the 2023 Champions League.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
