CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777392670
OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,FThe England defender has been
OL,7,Frestricted by injuries to only 16
OL,8,Fappearances for the club this season
OL,9,Fand is the second long-serving player
OL,10,Fto announce his impending departure
OL,11,Fafter Bernardo Silva.
OL,13,FIn an emotional video, Stones said of
OL,14,Fhis time at the Etihad: "It's been my
OL,15,Fhome for the past 10 years, and it
OL,16,Fwill be my home for the rest of my
OL,17,Flife.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
