OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777392670
OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,F"I came as a kid and I'm leaving as a
OL,7,Fman. I've become a father, a husband
OL,8,Fand, on the pitch, a very fulfilled
OL,9,Fplayer, living all my dreams out and
OL,10,Flifting all the things I came here to
OL,11,Fachieve.
OL,13,F"At the start of my career here I
OL,14,Fnever thought I'd be in this position
OL,15,F` firstly, to achieve everything, but
OL,16,Fto have the love, the bond, with
OL,17,Feveryone. Every dream has been smashed
OL,18,Fout the park."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@NO]
