PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777392670
OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,FStones, who has been capped 87 times
OL,7,Fby England, began his career with his
OL,8,Fhometown club Barnsley before moving
OL,9,Fon to Everton in 2013.
OL,11,FHis form at Goodison Park persuaded
OL,12,FCity to shell out nearly #50million,
OL,13,Fthe second highest transfer fee paid
OL,14,Ffor a defender at the time, and it was
OL,15,Fmeeting Guardiola that sealed the deal
OL,16,Ffor Stones.
OL,18,F"I don't think it would have been
OL,19,Fanywhere (near) as successful if it
OL,20,Fwasn't for him," said Stones.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777392670
OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,F"The first time that I met him, I left
OL,7,Fthat moment and knew that it was what
OL,8,FI wanted to do, where I wanted to be,
OL,9,Fplaying under the best manager in the
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,F"I'm so grateful I've been able to
OL,13,Fspend so long with him, win everything
OL,14,Fwith him, and share and have so many
OL,15,Fincredible moments together."
OL,17,FStones will hope to finish up his time
OL,18,Fat the Etihad with more silverware as
OL,19,FCity chase Premier League and FA Cup
OL,20,Fglory.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@]O]
