OL,3,CJohn Stones to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cat the end of the season
OL,6,F"I don't think it would have been
OL,7,Fanywhere (near) as successful if it
OL,8,Fwasn't for him," Stones said of the
OL,9,FCatalan in a video on Instagram.
OL,11,F"The first time that I met him, I left
OL,12,Fthat moment and knew that it was what
OL,13,FI wanted to do, where I wanted to be,
OL,14,Fplaying under the best manager in the
OL,15,Fworld.
OL,17,F"I'm so grateful I've been able to
OL,18,Fspend so long with him, win everything
OL,19,Fwith him, and share and have so many
OL,20,Fincredible moments together."
